abstract: NFL Roundup; Cleveland Browns organization decides not to take any immediate disciplinary action in aftermath of team quarterback Johnny Manziel's being pulled over by police for domestic matter; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: Manziel was pulled over by the police in Avon, Ohio, after a witness said a person was trying to jump from his speeding vehicle. Manziel admitted having consumed alcohol before the incident.

headline.main: Browns’ Johnny Manziel Avoids Charges After Dispute With Girlfriend
headline.print_headline: Browns’ Manziel Avoids Charges After Dispute With Girlfriend
